		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_65267393"><p>He should make a claim for transport costs &amp; similar. In the UK we have the small claims courts for this sort of thing; however I do not know how much of a legal leg he has to stand on. It is not clear if he had been told in advance that he was banned. This is a case where the use of a <a href="https://ico.org.uk/for-organisations/uk-gdpr-guidance-and-resources/subject-access-requests/a-guide-to-subject-access/" title="ico.org.uk">subject (data) access request under the GDPR</a> [ico.org.uk] would help a lot.</p></div>
